trans-unit.source: Represents a text effect that can be applied to text objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en text-effekt som kan brukes til tekstobjekter.

trans-unit.source: The TextEffect object allows you to add effects, such as animations, to text objects, such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>, and <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: TextEffect-objektet kan du legge til effekter, for eksempel animasjoner, tekstobjekter, slik som <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>, og <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>
